In this practical we will creating the telegram bot using python and the telepot package.

steps :-

1)Go to botfather in telegram app/web.

2)give commands
  /start - to start the BotFather bot
	/newbot - to create you own bot
	give name to your bot like "bbot" is mine.
	give username to your bot like "b22500bot" is mine.
	Now you will get a token to access HTTP API. 

3)Install telepot package in python to code the bot in python.

4)Write python bot code and run.

5)Send message to bot and bot will give response.
